> Basic app of ATM operations for single user
> ATM Simulator will simulate behaviour of the ATM
> Declare Private variables

Functional Req:
> Fixed Acc : pre create a single bank account with :
    > acc no : 12345678(long)
    > Pin : 1234 (int)
    > Balance : 10,000.00 (float)

> Login with PIN 
    > max 3 attempts

> Menu operations
    > Check Balance
    > Deposit Money
    > Withdraw Money
    > Exit

> Validations :
    > withdraw should not allow the balance to go below 500
    > deposit and witdraw amounts should be positive

